params.userPromptTemplate:
任务目标：{{goal}}
输出数量：{{count}}
来源列表(JSON)：{{sources}}

请按以下步骤执行：
1) 调用 dailyhot.fetch_topics，输入 baseUrl/sources/perSourceLimit
2) 调用 topic.evaluate_candidates，输入 candidates/goal/evaluatorId/count
3) 最终输出 final，严格匹配目标 JSON 结构

重要约束：
- 仅输出 JSON（通过 final.output 返回）
- selected 按优先级排序
- 若目标明确要求“只返回抖音”，selected 必须仅包含 douyin

目标 JSON 结构：{"selected":[{"rank":1,"title":"","source":"","sourceName":"","score":0-100,"reason":"","expected":{"exposure":0,"plays":0,"fans":0},"url":""}],"summary":"","discarded":[{"title":"","reason":""}]}
